            I have a passion for functional design and data and use this space
            to showcase current / past projects. Outside of tech,
            these designs come in the form of <%= link_to "routesetting", "https://thecliffsclimbing.com/blog/2016/6/24/meet-the-new-setters-marc-and-bo" %>.
          </p>
          <p>
            Check out my <%= link_to "work", "/work" %> or find me through
            the social links below.
          </p>
          <p class="shaded-teal cta">
            If you'd like to collaborate on your next project or just want to chat - reach out.
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:marc.akbar@gmail.com" class="btn"><i class="material-icons left">mail</i>EMAIL</a>
          <a href="images/Akbar_Marc_resume.pdf" class="btn" download><i class="material-icons left">file_download</i>RESUME</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="full-width center-horiz bottom">
  <%= erb :footer %>
